import React from 'react'

import MessagesRoutes from './messages_/MessagesRoutes'
import ProfileRoutes from './profile/ProfileRoutes'
import PostRoutes from './post_/PostRoutes'
import SettingsRoutes from './settings_/SettingsRoutes'

export default () => (
    <>
        <MessagesRoutes unreadMessagesNumber={unreadMessagesNumber}/>
        <ProfileRoutes />
        <PostRoutes />
        <SettingsRoutes />
    </>
)
